	------
	Rule: Unpack
	------
	Otavio R. Piske
	------
	Jan, 2013
	
Description

	Uncompress a tarball file (gzip or bzip2 only).
	
Element 

	Name: unpack

Attributes

	format: the file format of the compressed file. Acceptable values are: tbz2 and tgz.
	source: the file to unpack
	
Example

----------------------------------------
<unpack format="tbz2" 
			source="${workdir}/${name}-${version}-bin.tar.bz2"/>
----------------------------------------